# NT R&D - Recovery & Containment Team
ghost-role-information-rct-field-lead-name = RCT Field Lead
ghost-role-information-rct-field-lead-description = You command a NanoTrasen R&D Recovery & Containment Team. Make the recover-or-abort call, hold override authority over the station, and answer only to the Directorate. Recover the asset intact; be impeccably polite while you do it.
ghost-role-information-rct-containment-name = RCT Containment Tech
ghost-role-information-rct-containment-description = You are the Recovery & Containment Team's specialist. Stabilise the hazard, deploy containment, and identify the asset. You are the reason this is a recovery team and not a deathsquad - keep it that way.
ghost-role-information-rct-operative-name = RCT Operative
ghost-role-information-rct-operative-description = You are muscle for a NanoTrasen R&D Recovery & Containment Team. Breach, give cover, and physically recover the asset under fire. Follow the Field Lead. Resistance is an inefficiency, not an insult.
ghost-role-information-rct-proctor-name = RCT Proctor
ghost-role-information-rct-proctor-description = You oversee a NanoTrasen R&D Recovery & Containment Team for the Directorate. Enforce discipline, keep the operation clean, and block any unilateral destroy-call. The asset is recovered intact, or there are consequences.
